===Pronunciation===
*ἄγω / agō / ag'-o
===Etymology===

*A primary verb; properly to lead; by implication to bring, drive, (reflexively) go, (specifically) pass (time), or (figuratively) induce: 
===Verb===
'''ἄγω'''

# [[be]], [[bring]] (forth), [[carry]], (let) [[go]], [[keep]], lead away, be open.